==Introduction==
The '''ReferenceGroup''' widget allows to group pages which links to given page by a specified property ("groupBy") and
displays a list of unique values for that property. The grouping property has to be of 'Page' type.

The widget is displayed on View and Edit pages.
The widget allows to apply different styles to rendered list.


==Definition==
<pre>
<concept name="{GROUP}">
  <structure>
    <property name="Property I"/>
    <property name="Property II"/>
    <property name="Property III"/>
    <property name="{REFERRING PROPERTY NAME}" refersTo="{TARGET}"/>
  </structure>
</concept>

<concept name="{SOURCE}">
  <structure>
    <property name="Property 1"/>
    <property name="Property 2"/>
    <property name="{GROUPING PROPERTY}" refersTo="{GROUP}"/>
    <property name="{REFERRING PROPERTY NAME}" refersTo="{TARGET}"/>
  </structure>
</concept>

<concept name="{TARGET}">
  <structure>
    <property name="Property A"/>
    <property name="Property B"/>
    <referenceGroup name="{REFERENCE NAME}" groupConcept="{GROUP}"  refersFrom="{SOURCE}"
               property="{REFERRING PROPERTY NAME}" groupBy="{GROUPING PROPERTY}"
               sortBy="{SORT PROPERTY}" sortOrder="{SORT ORDER}"
               label="{LABEL}" format="{FORMAT}" icon="{ICON}">
      <columns>
        <column name="{COLUMN NAME}"/>
        <column name="{COLUMN NAME}"/>
        <column name="{COLUMN NAME}"/>
      </columns>
    </referenceGroup>
  </structure>
</concept>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {SOURCE}
| A name of the Source Concept.
|-
! {TARGET}
| A name of the Target Concept.
|-
! {GROUP}
| A name of the Group Concept.
|-
! {REFERRING PROPERTY NAME}
| A name of the property of 'Page' type in the Source Concept which refers to the Target Concept.
|-
! {GROUPING PROPERTY}
| A name of the property of 'Page' type in the Source Concept which is to be used to group references to the Target Concept.
|-
! {REFERENCE NAME}
| A name of the ReferenceGroup.
|-
! {LABEL}
| A label of the ReferenceGroup, if not set the {REFERENCE NAME} is used as a label.
|-
! {SORT PROPERTY}
| The name of the property to be used for sorting purposes
|-
! {SORT ORDER}
| The order of the sorting. The following values are allowed:
* ''desc''
* ''asc''
|-
! {FORMAT}
| A format type used to render referring Source Concept pages. The following options are allowed:
* table. The "table" layout displays a table with referring pages. The first column displays a Source page name, and the following columns display the values of the properties defined in the {COLUMNS} attribute.
* list. The "link" layout displays a list of referring pages. The main list heading displays a Source page name, and under it the values of the properties defined in the {COLUMNS} attribute.
* link. The "link" layout displays simple list of links to the referring Source pages.
* gallery. The "gallery" layout displays gallery of images/logos associated with the pages.
* gallerylist. The "gallerylist" layout displays a list of images/logos associated with the pages with the values of the properties defined in the {COLUMNS} attribute..
|-
! {COLUMN NAME}
| A name of the column to be displayed next to the page name.
|}



==Example==
<pre>
<concept name="Focus Area">                                   <!- Group Concept -->
  <structure>
    <property name="Image" mandatory="true" width="40"/>
    <property name="Acronym" mandatory="true"/>
    <property name="Title" mandatory="true"/>
    <property name="Description" mandatory="true"/>
  </structure>
</concept>

<concept name="Capability Configuration">                     <!-- Source Concept -->
  <structure>
    <property name="Short name" mandatory="true"/>
    <property name="Is led by" multiplicity="one"/>
    <property name="Is managed by" refersTo="CWIX Nation">    <!-- Referring Page Property -->
    <property name="Is interested in" refersTo="Focus Area">  <!-- Grouping property -->
    </group>
  </structure>
</concept>

<concept name="CWIX Nation" >                                 <!-- Target Concept -->
  <structure>
    <property name="Flag"/>
    <property name="Country code"/>
    <referenceGroups name="Focus Areas" groupConcept="Focus Area" refersFrom="Capability Configuration" property="Is managed by" groupBy="Is interested in" format="gallery"/>
  </structure>
</concept>
</pre>


==User Interface==
The "ReferenceGroup" widget is displayed on View and Edit Pages of the Target Concept ("CWIX Nation" in the example above).
